  "description": "A close-up, overhead shot of a vibrant orange tulip flower. The petals curl inward, creating a tunnel-like view into the flower's center.  Inside, a dark brown/black stigma and anthers are clearly visible against a backdrop of green floral tissue.  The focus is extremely tight on the tulip, with blurred shapes of other flowers and greenery in the background, creating a shallow depth of field. The lighting is soft and warm, highlighting the texture of the petals.",
